media:group.media:title: The Rise and Fall of Social Repose - (Richie Giese)
media:group.media:description:
Social Repose, a content creator with much potential, ruined by his inability to remain faithful. His journey through YouTube serves as a warning that good content must be matched with appealing traits in order to retain a viewer base.
